<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>“周末戏苑”柳子戏</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200828/43afdf5aed6e488c91f1e48a9d877c49.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
